data.description: PRIDE IN OWNERSHIP! Welcome to Ridge Crest! Excellent location! Close to HWYs, walkable to parks and schools! This 2 story, 4 bedroom home offers 2 sizeable living rooms, and is fully finished, top to bottom! NEWER Roof. NEWER AC. NEW interior paint! NEW flooring throughout! NEW toilets. NEW fans. NEW sinks. Stainless steel appliances STAY. XLarge Pantry space. Main Floor Laundry. Skylights, bringing in TONS of natural light. Vaulted ceilings with a main floor gas fireplace! The master offers a Jacuzzi Jetted Tub, with a fully updated 5-piece master bath and walk in closet! This home boasts a second soaking tub too. A completely Private basement, with a family/game room, seconding operating gas fireplace, oversized full bathroom! Flagstone patio, hammock area, and mature landscaping.
